    "diffSummary": "Added the types/ layer (Credentials + Cookie + CredentialError in credentials.rs; AccountId, AccountProfile, CredentialSummary in account.rs) with no zca-rust dependency, and the command/ layer with import_credentials, which parses a ZaloDataExtractor JSON export, validates required fields, and returns a non-secret CredentialSummary (lengths + counts only). lib.rs declares both modules and registers the command. A minimal frontend (+page.svelte) pastes JSON, invokes import_credentials, and renders the summary. Credential token values (imei/cookie/userAgent) are never logged or returned across IPC, and nothing is persisted (Phase 3). Six cargo tests cover valid import, malformed JSON, empty cookies, blank imei, and the language default.",
    "changedFiles": [
        "src-tauri/src/lib.rs",
        "src-tauri/src/command/mod.rs",
